{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262090/extras/OGORAICON.png?t=1736852672\" /><br>Having caused the Wizard a massive headache, you (and your ill-prepared companion) are temporarily banished from your home to play in the garden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As an enchanted piece of furniture, you can guide both friends and foes through the twists and turns of the mysterious garden - <strong>Ogora!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262090/extras/banner_1.png?t=1736852672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262090/extras/OGORA_STEAM_GIF_5.gif?t=1736852672\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the magical garden of Ogora and test your mind (and your luck) against your enchanted friends - while the Wizard tries to get a moment of peace!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover secrets within the hedges of the garden (or make a path of your own!). But be careful, not everyone in the garden will aid you!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262090/extras/banner_3.png?t=1736852672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262090/extras/OGORA_STEAM_GIF_4.gif?t=1736852672\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Draft new powers, ancient spells, or hoard your explosives for those pesky pillows and ornery ottomans that block your path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experiment with a massive number of unique cards, heavily guarded spells, and hidden trinkets \u2013 seriously, some of these are pretty secret.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragra